----------------------------------------------------------------
                        size
----------------------------------------------------------------

0=0
1=0.25rem
2=0.5rem
3=1rem
4=1.5rem
5=3rem
auto = auto(margin only)

Note: m-3 (margin 1rem on all side)
Note: mt-2 (margin-top 0.5)
Note: px-4 (padding left+right 1.5rem)

--> w-25 (25%)
--> w-50 (50%)
--> w-100 (100%)
--> w-auto (auto)

--> h-25 (25%)
--> h-50 (50%)
--> h-100 (100%)
--> h-auto (auto)

