----------------------------------------------------------------
                        Grid
----------------------------------------------------------------

--> col
--> col-*
--> col-sm-*
--> col-lg-*
--> col-md-*
--> col-xl-*
--> col-xxl-*

Note : MIPM

--> (extra small) .col- -> <576px
--> (small) .col-sm-*-> >= 576px
--> (medium) .col-md-*-> >= 768px
--> (large) .col-lg-* -> >=992px
--> (Extra large) .col-xl-* -> >=992px
--> (Extra Extra large) .col-xxl-* -> >=1200px